  "short_description": "Hide in the shadows and infiltrate enemy bases as a stealth specialist. Gust of Wind immerses you in a post-apocalyptic world of dilapidated mines and rusted sail ships, where you use the gadgets and routes available to complete your objectives with as little attention as possible.",
